                "NewScoring": 1,
                "SurveyMetaDescription": "Large language models (LLMs) can generate text that is almost indistinguishable from human writing. Given their increasing popularity and availability, as well as their continuous improvement, people\u2019s scepticism towards the authenticity of written content intensifies. This research aims to find out how people may modify written text to signal human authorship and distinguish it from LLM-generated content.",
