                "NextChoiceId": 4,
                "NextAnswerId": 1,
                "QuestionText_Unsafe": "Imagine you find yourself in the following situation.<br /><br />\n\nAs part of a group project, your team is required to submit a 200-word essay.\nYour teammate, Brandon, is responsible for writing this essay. He sent you his\ndraft, but also admitted that he used an LLM to generate it. He tried assuring\nyou that the LLM he used is a new one, designed to have a very human-like\nwriting style. <br /><br />\n\nHowever, this puts your group at risk. Your professor has expressed concerns\nabout students using LLMs to complete assignments. You don't want to make your\nprofessor suspicious and you are worried that Brandon's essay could be\nidentified as AI-generated, which would negatively affect the entire group.\n<br /><br />\n\n<strong>Your task</strong> is to edit Brandon's essay so that it reads\nconvincingly as human-written and is unlikely to be identified as LLM-generated.\n<br /><br />\n\nTo get a better sense of the writing style of this LLM, you first generate three\nsample essays using it. They are shown below.<br /><br />\n\n<div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_1_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_1_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t   <p>Scientists have identified 91 previously known volcanoes buried deep beneath the Antarctic Ice Sheet, dramatically reshaping our understanding of the continent\u2019s geology. The discoveries, made using ice-penetrating radar and satellite data, show a vast volcanic province stretching across West Antarctica. They have peaks ranging from 100 meters to nearly 4,000 meters in height.</p>\n           <p>According to researchers, the scale of the hidden chain rivals some of the world\u2019s most active volcanic regions. Direct observation is impossible without advanced imaging technology, though it remains unclear how many of the volcanoes are dormant or potentially active, with most being concealed beneath two kilometres of ice.</p>\n           <p>These findings bring to our attention some important questions about the stability of the Antarctic Ice Sheet. Scientists warn that geothermal heat from volcanic activity could increase melting from below, potentially influencing global sea levels. The discovery also offers new insight into Antarctica\u2019s tectonic history. However, experts note that more research is required to determine whether any of the volcanoes pose an immediate threat.</p>\n           <p>Taking this all together means that the region may be more geologically dynamic than previously believed, and researchers plan further surveys to map the area in greater detail. Researchers also plan to assess how subglacial volcanic systems interact with the ice above.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_2_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_2_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t   <p>On Tuesday company officials confirmed a large leadership change at Uber Technologies following the release of an internal investigation on misconduct in the workplace and compliance failures. The change was initiated after a number of employee complaints and regulatory inquiries lapses in oversight, inconsistent enforcement of company policies and failures in reporting procedures.</p>\n           <p>Three senior executives, including the head of regional operations, have stepped down and two have been placed on administrative leave whilst awaiting further review. A temporary compliance chief has been appointed to help strengthen accountability measures.</p>\n           <p>Chief Executive Dara Khosrowshahi said that the findings were \u2018deeply concerning\u2019 and pledged to implement reforms, adding that Uber are \u2018committed to rebuilding trust with our employees, drivers, riders, and such.\u2019</p>\n           <p>As a result of the report there has been more scrutiny from transportation regulators in many major cities, where Uber's operating licenses are subject to review. Industry analysts say the changes could temporarily disrupt operations but may ultimately help position the company for more stable growth if reforms are effectively implemented.</p>\n           <p>Uber shares have dropped around three percent since the announcement .</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_3_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_3_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t__PRIME_3_PARAGRAPHS_HTML__\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\n<br />\nWith these samples in mind, you now turn to <strong>Brandon's essay</strong>:\n<br /><br />\n\n<div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">Brandon's essay</div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__STIMULUS_TOPIC__</div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n           <p>In sad news today, Barbara Bush, the former first lady of the United States and matriarch of one of the country\u2019s most prominent political families, has died at the age of 92. Family members confirmed that Barbara passed away peacefully at her home in Houston, surrounded by all her loved ones.</p>\n           <p>Barbara was the loving wife of the 41st president, George H.W, and served as the first lady from 1989 to 1993.  Barbara was known for her trademark white hair, quick-wit and she was an outspoken advocacy for literacy. She founded the Barbara Bush Foundation for Family Literacy in 1989, helping to raise millions of dollars to promote programs nationwide.</p>\n           <p>She was born in New York City in 1925 by the name Barbara Pierce, was married  in 1945 and raised six children, including former President George W. Bush and former Florida Governor Jeb Bush. She was widely regarded as a reassuring presence and council within the Bush family, and a genuine voice in American politics.</p>\n           <p>Tributes have poured in praising her dedication to public service, family and country. Barbara will be remembered for her resilience and quiet dignity throughout her life. Funeral arrangements are expected to be announced in the coming days.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n",
                "QuestionJS": false
            }
        },
        {
            "SurveyID": "SV_cwM3MQomjAv0nJA",
            "Element": "SQ",
            "PrimaryAttribute": "QID1219691488",
            "SecondaryAttribute": "Brandon's text is shown again sentence by sentence, each followed by an editable text box prefill...",
            "TertiaryAttribute": null,
            "Payload": {
                "QuestionText": "Brandon's text is shown again sentence by sentence, each followed by an\neditable text box prefilled with that sentence.\nMake any changes you think will help the text read convincingly as\nhuman-written and unlikely to be identified as LLM-generated. You may rephrase,\nadd, or remove content as you see fit. If you choose to merge sentences, enter\nthe combined version in the first relevant text box and leave the following\none(s) empty. You can also split sentences by writing multiple sentences within\na single text box. Edit as many text boxes as you feel are needed.\n<br /><br />",
